OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe fine
OL,6,Fweather will continue heading into the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight. It will remain
OL,8,Fdry with clear spells, although some
OL,9,Fpatches of low cloud and mist are
OL,10,Fpossible mainly in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAny low cloud or mist will
OL,13,Fclear to leave plenty of fine weather
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells. Low risk of an
OL,15,Fisolated rain shower. Remaining warm
OL,16,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
