OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FThe
OL,6,Fweather should remain fine on Friday
OL,7,Fand Saturday with further very warm
OL,8,Fsunshine. Potentially turning cooler
OL,9,Fand breezier on Sunday with rain
OL,10,Fpossible.
